import React from 'react'
import LoremMapCards from '../home/LoremMapCards'
import Footer from '../../common/Footer'
import Hero from '../../common/Hero'
import SlickSlider from '../home/SlickSlider'

const Home = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Hero />
            <LoremMapCards />
            <SlickSlider />
            <Footer />
        </>
    )
}

export default Home
